ZH: 请不要随地丢弃菸蒂。
EN: Please do not litter cigarette butts everywhere.

ZH: 这个垃圾桶里满是菸蒂。
EN: This trash bin is filled with cigarette butts.

ZH: 他不小心踩到了一个菸蒂。
EN: He accidentally stepped on a cigarette butt.

ZH: 这条街上到处都是菸蒂。
EN: There are cigarette butts everywhere on this street.

ZH: 我看到一个人掐灭菸蒂后扔掉了。
EN: I saw someone extinguish a cigarette butt and throw it away.

ZH: 你可以把菸蒂放在这个灰缸里。
EN: You can put the cigarette butt in this ashtray.

ZH: 我捡起了地上的菸蒂并丢进了垃圾桶。
EN: I picked up the cigarette butt from the ground and threw it into the trash bin.

ZH: 这是地球上最普遍的垃圾之一，菸蒂。
EN: This is one of the most common types of litter on Earth, cigarette butts.

ZH: 这个公园禁止吸烟和丢弃菸蒂。
EN: Smoking and littering cigarette butts are prohibited in this park.

ZH: 我从街道上捡起了那个菸蒂。
EN: I picked up the cigarette butt from the street.

ZH: 角落里堆积着许多菸蒂。
EN: There are many cigarette butts piled up in the corner.

ZH: 菸蒂会对环境造成严重的污染。
EN: Cigarette butts can cause severe pollution to the environment.

ZH: 他把菸蒂放进了口袋里，没有找到垃圾桶。
EN: He put the cigarette butt in his pocket as he couldn't find a trash bin.

ZH: 这个街区经常有人在路边丢弃菸蒂。
EN: People often litter cigarette butts on the roadside in this neighborhood.

ZH: 不要践踏菸蒂，这很危险。
EN: Do not step on cigarette butts, it's dangerous.

ZH: 这个公共场所禁止抛弃菸蒂。
EN: It is prohibited to discard cigarette butts in this public place.

ZH: 我经常看到人们随意丢弃菸蒂。
EN: I often see people casually throwing away cigarette butts.

ZH: 菸蒂会引发火灾，请小心处理。
EN: Cigarette butts can cause fires, please handle them with care.

ZH: 别把菸蒂随手扔掉，这对环境不好。
EN: Don't just throw away cigarette butts, it's not good for the environment.
